author: jwross
msg: ARIES-708: org.apache.aries.util pom should point to java6-parent, not java5-parent

Set org.apache.aries.util pom back to java5-parent. Set java5-parent project pom to accept 1.6 source but still target 1.5. This results in no @Override compile errors on implemented interface methods but still enforces java 5 compatibility on org.apache.aries.util.
